### Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe the problem.

Blazor is making changes to the DOM that works most of the time. But sometimes you mess up and do something that triggered thousands of unnecessary changes in the DOM and this could be very hard to detect. 


### Describe the solution you'd like

I would like to have some tooling that makes it easy to see which changes are done in the DOM via Blazor. Both how many changes are done on every update, and some detailed log on exact which changes were made. This would make it easier to troubleshoot and detect any potential performance issues.


### Additional context

I have created a super simple JavaScript tool that logs every change in the DOM. Not perfect, but better than nothing:

```javascript
function startMutationMonitoring(elementId = document, outputId) {
    // Get the target node
    const targetNode = elementId === document ? document : document.getElementById(elementId);

    // Get the element that we'll output the logs to
    const monitorLog = outputId ? document.getElementById(outputId) : null;

    // Options for the observer (which mutations to observe)
    const config = { attributes: true, childList: true, subtree: true, characterData: true };

    // Callback function to execute when mutations are observed
    const callback = function (mutationsList, observer) {
        const timestamp = new Date().toLocaleTimeString();

        for (let mutation of mutationsList) {
            let outputText = `${timestamp} Mutation type: ${mutation.type}`;

            if (mutation.type === 'childList') {
                for (let addedNode of mutation.addedNodes) {
                    outputText += '\nAdded Node id: ' + addedNode.id;
                    outputText += '\nAdded Node HTML: ' + addedNode.outerHTML;
                }

                for (let removedNode of mutation.removedNodes) {
                    outputText += '\nRemoved Node id: ' + removedNode.id;
                    outputText += '\nRemoved Node HTML: ' + removedNode.outerHTML;
                }

            } else if (mutation.type === 'attributes') {
                outputText += ', attribute changed: ' + mutation.attributeName;
                outputText += ', new value: ' + mutation.target.getAttribute(mutation.attributeName);
            } else if (mutation.type === 'characterData') {
                outputText += ', content changed: ' + mutation.target.data;
            }

            outputText += '\n\n';

            if (monitorLog) {
                let textNode = document.createTextNode(outputText);
                monitorLog.appendChild(textNode);
            } else {
                console.log(outputText);
            }
        }
    };

    // Create an observer instance linked to the callback function
    const observer = new MutationObserver(callback);

    // Start observing the target node for configured mutations
    observer.observe(targetNode, config);
}
```

